## Platform Repository
Each platform has it's implementation class which implements special PlatformRepository interface to access it's data.
To connect implementation I should use di_config.php to set initialization logic.
name of the key in array should be "platform.<platform_name>"

## Youtube Set-up
Ref: https://developers.google.com/youtube/v3/docs/
Ref: https://developers.google.com/api-client-library/php/start/get_started
I need to create API project to get my credentials

To upload video I need auth Token: I can get it via following this guide:
https://developers.google.com/youtube/v3/guides/auth/server-side-web-apps

